      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARLEY BOY (3) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at The Gardens. Can make amends this time. IBROX MAVERICK (1) missed the frame last time when sixth (23.18) at The Gardens but prior to that had two placings in a row. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Worth following up. LAKOTA COURTNEY (6) placed two back in a Grade 5 at Richmond Straight then backed that up with a third (22.58) over 388m at this track last time. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Well placed here and should do much better. IN THE QUEUE (8) has claims fresh from a recent placing.",
